No. 09-1097. Antonio Peck, a Minor, By and Through His Parents and Next Friends, Jo Anne Peck and Kenley Lester Peck, Petitioner v. Baldwinsville Central School District, et al. 560 U.S. 959, 130 S. Ct. 3386,

177 L. Ed. 2d 315,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 4658. June 7, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 351 Fed. Appx. 477.
